THE MAGNOLIA. THE WESLEY A. GOVE. THE JOHN A. HUGHES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. October 24, 1922.) No. 37. Foley & Martin, of New York City (George V. A. McCloskey, of New *1021York City, of counsel), for appellant. Horace L. Cheyney, of New York City, for the John A. Hughes.

Before ROGERS, MANTON, and MAYER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
